snippet.title: CAVE SHOOTER | A game you can’t miss out in 2021 | Shooting Mobile Game
snippet.description:
"#Casual #Shooting #MobileGame

Cave Shooter is a popular idle shooting game.

Playing with one hand, mix match gear & skills to craft your own playing style! 

⚡Download on Google Play / App Store:
https://eyou.io/caveshooter

🦕 Official Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/caveshooter
🦕 Official Discord: https://discord.gg/bmydT2k8F3
🦕 Official Website: https://caveshooter.eyougame.com/"
